data.description: Come see this great looking home in the Stagecoach estates subdivision in Autryville before its too late! Built in 2022, this home features an open floor plan with a large kitchen island, perfect for entertaining. Its a short drive to Fort Liberty and the heart of Fayetteville. This home offers you country living at its finest!
